{"tid":602991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駕車撞單車男 休班警罰款","createTime":"2018-03-23T10:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T14:56:47.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"143c557a170595c4c5754fd25d2a36a17d437d4f","tid":602991,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180323/20340370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F20340370&d=5Az3%2Bs1K3u9mHTYSG2JC3ozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=676cbd43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180323%2F20340370&h=96b2b0e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180323/20340370</a><br />\n<br />\n駕車撞單車男<br />\n休班警罰款<br />\n<br />\n法庭   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180323/large/a1803a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180323%2Flarge%2Fa1803a.gif&h=2255e6a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告陳健珩不小心駕駛罪成，被判罰款及停牌。陳善南攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】休班警駕車轉入尖沙嘴海運大廈停車場時，撞傷踏單車送外賣的五旬男子，令他右腳3隻腳趾骨折。休班警否認危險駕駛導致他人嚴重身體受傷罪，案件昨開審。裁判官裁定休班警罪脫，但不小心駕駛罪名成立，判罰款4,000元及停牌一年。<br />\n<br />\n55歲事主張德全供稱，去年7月15日踏單車送完外賣後，踏單車沿港威大道北行，至海運大廈停車場出入口時，被告陳健珩（45歲）從對面行車線轉彎撞到單車，單車損壞，他右腳3隻腳趾骨折，留院兩日，另獲95日病假，經打石膏及看跌打後完全康復。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方指被告當時打算轉入停車場，但前面有大貨車，亦有七人車從停車場駛出，令他的視線受阻，未能看到事主。裁判官相信被告一時疏忽才犯案，裁定他不小心駕駛罪成。辯方求情指被告加入警隊26年，任警車車長15年，事後沒再駕駛，改任巡邏工作，停牌令過後才可再考牌。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC144/18<br />\n■記者戴國輝"},{"pid":"b472c4163dbabe8d8b3ff8274db82b90c7e7e2b7","tid":602991,"uid":63950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T10:56:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"744918b40e2a664861bc0be0dae884ffb1d290ec","tid":602991,"uid":1414,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:01:22.000Z","msg":"死單車狗 要死死遠啲"},{"pid":"6039e4e11701721122bc54fbf8f3d6d40b2122bc","tid":602991,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T11:02:28.000Z","msg":"照樣返工等長糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2ee88b0482f7c1f572e8ecd364116d9faae52c","tid":602991,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"差人揸車唔洗你教"},{"pid":"83dfa5022be3343a20f845b70077455d408c2d40","tid":602991,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb2ee88b0482f7c1f572e8ecd364116d9faae52c","tid":602991,"uid":81995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T12:13:51.000Z","msg":"差人揸車唔洗你教"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"差人揸車<span style=\"color: blue;\">撞人</span>唔洗你教"}]}